57
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:11,710
Yes, yes.

58
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:15,120
Song Dynasty ceramics are
particularly popular these days.

59
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,450
They're in high demand.

60
00:03:16,590 --> 00:03:17,120
Alright.

61
00:03:17,520 --> 00:03:18,590
But in this field,

62
00:03:19,079 --> 00:03:20,400
the waters run deep.

63
00:03:20,400 --> 00:03:21,280
7.5 million.

64
00:03:21,280 --> 00:03:22,520
Eight million from you again.

65
