Alright, now it's 10 million yuan

77
00:03:47,120 --> 00:03:49,030
from Mr. No. 888.

78
00:03:49,840 --> 00:03:51,750
Any more bids?

79
00:03:52,560 --> 00:03:54,190
Alright, 10 million yuan,

80
00:03:54,470 --> 00:03:55,560
going once.

81
00:03:56,190 --> 00:03:57,360
Ten million yuan,

82
00:03:57,630 --> 00:03:58,630
going twice.

83
